title: Weather v2.0 - Simple WordPress Shortcode & Widget
description:
Simple Weather is a beautiful weather plugin, which displays the current weather via shortcodes or via widgets. Add a simple, yet very useful feature to your website with this stylish plugin. Your visitors will know right away how to plan their schedule, happy to know the weather is on their side. Simple Weather is based on OpenWeatherMap.org. Contains external links.

To install:

1. Upload to wordpress plugin directory
2. Activate through plugin menu in wp-admin
